compute the variability.

00:05:52.540 --> 00:05:55.150 align:middle line:84%
And then you look on the
margin about whether to add

00:05:55.150 --> 00:05:58.390 align:middle line:90%
or subtract one more.

00:05:58.390 --> 00:06:03.250 align:middle line:84%
And you look at its variability
relative to this village

00:06:03.250 --> 00:06:05.530 align:middle line:90%
