stream which is low when--

00:06:16.050 --> 00:06:19.570 align:middle line:84%
well, say high when the
rest of the village is low.

00:06:19.570 --> 00:06:21.690 align:middle line:84%
So that's kind of the
way the diversification

00:06:21.690 --> 00:06:28.370 align:middle line:84%
