I'm sorry.

00:50:14.330 --> 00:50:16.220 align:middle line:90%
The pictures are too small.

00:50:16.220 --> 00:50:22.040 align:middle line:84%
But what's plotted over here are
net cash inflows or outflows,

00:50:22.040 --> 00:50:26.600 align:middle line:84%
along with, say, a deposit
when you have a net inflow,

00:50:26.600 --> 00:50:30.330 align:middle line:84%
or a withdrawal when
